At first when I read the title "The filter bubble'' I was confused because I never heard that phrase before but when I started to read the article I found that The filter bubble is the thing that am exposed to, all of the time.
The filter bubble is centered and involved  in special in the internet sites and programs. It shows us the things we want to see and the reports and news that we are interested in that happening because when have involved in the internet we added all the topics that we wanted to search for so the filter bubble have took that history of our searching engine and worked according to it.
In addition The filter bubble can work according to our site too, for example it would show you the weather in your  specific area .
I think the filter bubble have facilitated our internet life because you just inter to your virtual life and the things you should interested in will bubble in front of you instantly.